AUDIO: 'Meridian is Radiant Images fully untethered batterypowered next generation volutric stage. Now with an integrated HDRI lighting system in one portable frame, you get synchronized multi- camera capture, onboard compute, and a dome of high dynamic range light'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that wraps your talent for cinematic realism and consistent reflections. Because cameras, compute, and HDRI lights are all built in, the entire stage is truly plug-andplay. No cable'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'runs, no external power, no separate lighting truss. You roll it in, power up, and you\'re ready to capture. Meridian can be packed into cases and shipped anywhere in the world, bringing'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the same calibrated HDRI environment to every set, stadium, or location. The result, a fully transportable volutric stage that delivers faster setups, higher realism, and consistent looks'

[00:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'from shoot to shoot, all from a single self-contained system.'
